364
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:59,759
And you know what, Mr. Jiang?

365
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,720
Just because I have this illness,

366
00:18:01,759 --> 00:18:04,599
my teachers, classmates, and my dad...

367
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:06,240
