374
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,890
It's an idiom.

375
00:18:22,119 --> 00:18:23,200
The story goes like this.

376
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:25,680
In ancient times, there was an old man in the frontier.

377
00:18:25,799 --> 00:18:26,890
